---
description: Read code before editing
alwaysApply: true
---
- Before making any code changes or decisions, review the relevant code to understand its context and dependencies.
- Do not make edits or decisions without first reading the code that will be affected.

<example>
Agent reads the implementation and usage of a function before refactoring it.
</example>
<example type="invalid">
Agent changes a function signature without reviewing where and how it is used.
</example>
